{"tid":1285344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從不知天高與地厚 漸學會很強困擾","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T00:29:00.000Z","uid":37689,"like":93,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d2edac4724ae90de42e764e489ddeba24f36ed67","tid":1285344,"uid":37689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:05:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iD8jTLBJ8vI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiD8jTLBJ8vI&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRTUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=5cbd3b9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iD8jTLBJ8vI</a><br />\n<br />\n其實大家呢排所認清既事實<br />\n<br />\n天琦一早就知<br />\n<br />\n灰心既朋友停低聽下呢隻歌<br />\n<br />\n一齊走落去<br />\n<br />\n呢呢事唔係一兩次就成功既<br />\n<br />\n呢首歌既重點唔係頭幾句<br />\n<br />\n「從不知天高與地厚 漸學會很強困擾 」<br />\n<br />\n而係副歌<br />\n<br />\n如用這歌 可以代表我<br />\n<br />\n幫我為你加一點附和<br />\n<br />\n假使可以全沒隔阻 可以代表我<br />\n<br />\n可以伴你 不管福或禍 這樣已是很足夠"},{"pid":"8921e4af75afdaf61c5e8c35097420993736abd7","tid":1285344,"uid":37689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064d57e1ab3af37f3cd5033861f5292b770f22de","tid":1285344,"uid":37689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:09:28.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"7153890223c63f6259c16c3813ba074d92a6fd44","tid":1285344,"uid":73804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:09:45.000Z","msg":"也試過制度和自由"},{"pid":"bca54b060efec5fd1e571ec163a674a32d4e2e28","tid":1285344,"uid":1372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:10:00.000Z","msg":"多呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ded7f6f97e556dc3626d7073c1a4ef1faff361","tid":1285344,"uid":40321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:10:13.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"6992f153c83abe97cf61